hi Search ctermfg=226 ctermbg=197 cterm=underline
hi Comment ctermfg=103 ctermbg=NONE
hi Matchparen ctermfg=226 ctermbg=197
hi Wildmenu ctermfg=123 ctermbg=NONE cterm=underline
